<p><strong>14. UPDATES AND CHANGES TO PRIVACY NOTICE.</strong> We may need to modify this Privacy Notice as the law or our data practices changes. If we make material changes, we will notify you of such changes by any reasonable means (e.g., notice on the
  Sites, email to the email address we have on file, etc.) prior to them becoming effective. Your continued use of the Site after receiving such notice means that you acknowledge and accept the revised Privacy&nbsp;Notice.
