<p>9. REASONS WHY YOUR ENTRY MIGHT BE AXED: (a) Your entry featured minors or any persons under the legal drinking age (except incidental and not part of the primary content.) C&#8217;mon guys, we all know you think your niece holding a beer bottle is cute, but
  we also know combining underage folks and beer is just a bad idea. (b) Your entry featured explicit nudity (by any person over and under the legal drinking age). Keep it in your pants&#8230;nobody needs to see that. (c) Your entry included disparaging context
