<p style="text-align:justify; margin:0in 0in 0.0001pt">&nbsp;</p>
<p style="text-align:justify; margin:0in 0in 0.0001pt"><span style="font-size:12pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">13.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <u>SPONSOR</u>: This Promotion is sponsored by Sierra Nevada Brewing Co., 1075 East 20th Street, Chico, California 95928. See </span>
  <a
    href="http://www.sierranevada.com" style="color:blue; text-decoration:underline"><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">www.sierranevada.com</span></a><span style="font-family:&quot;Times New Roman&quot;,serif">.&nbsp; This Promotion is not in any way sponsored, endorsed or administered by, or associated with, Facebook, Instagram or&nbsp;Twitter.</span></span>
